OL,6,FSarah's daughter is one of 2,045
OL,7,Fadults with and who are currently
OL,8,Flocked up in inpatient units.
OL,10,FAn ITV News investigation with
OL,11,Flearning disability charity Mencap has
OL,12,Funcovered it's costing more than half
OL,13,Fa billion pounds a year to lock people
OL,14,Flike Sarah's daughter up in mental
OL,15,Fhealth hospitals.
