OL,6,FWendy and her colleagues have set up
OL,7,Fan. Last year they were able to
OL,8,Fprevent 53 people from being admitted
OL,9,Finto hospital.
OL,11,FThe cost of running the six-person
OL,12,Funit for that year was the same as the
OL,13,Fcost of keeping one person in a mental
OL,14,Fhospital for 12 months.
OL,16,FWendy and her team are not only
OL,17,Fworking to prevent inappropriate
OL,18,Fhospital admissions but they also help
OL,19,Fand support people to live independent
OL,20,Fand fulfilled lives in the community.
