OL,6,FDaisy is one of them. She is 19 and
OL,7,Fautistic.
OL,9,FWhen we met her she told us her
OL,10,Fexperience as an inpatient had been
OL,11,Fvery traumatic, but she was keen to
OL,12,Fshow us how her life has been
OL,13,Ftransformed now that she is .
OL,15,F"A lot of the time no, you can't
OL,16,Fshower by yourself, someone has to be
OL,17,Fsupervising you ... It makes you feel
OL,18,Fvery undignified," she said.
