OL,6,F"I felt very distressed a lot of the
OL,7,Ftime and isolated and lost because
OL,8,Fthere just wasn't the staff there to
OL,9,Fsupport me and make me feel better.
OL,11,F"I was having a meltdown and they
OL,12,Fdidn't understand, so instead they
