OL,6,FMarie Caulfield, parliamentary under-
OL,7,Fsecretary at the Department of Health,
OL,8,Ftold ITV News that people in the
OL,9,Fsystem have often been in hospital
OL,10,F"for many, many years".
OL,12,F"Just simply discharging them into the
OL,13,Fcommunity is not a simple process,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,F"For each and every one of those
OL,17,Fpatients we have plans in place on how
